---
import BaseHead from '../components/BaseHead.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <BaseHead title="About · Barış Gürbüzler" description="Co-founder & CEO of Hardal. Based in Barcelona." />
  </head>
  <body>
    <Header />
    <main>
      <div class="page-header">
        <h1 class="page-title">About</h1>
      </div>

      <div class="prose">
        <p>
          I'm Barış. Originally from Antalya, studied in Istanbul, and now 
          living in Barcelona with my wife Göz, our cat Kiwi, and our dog Miso.
        </p>

        <p>
          I co-founded <a href="https://usehardal.com" target="_blank">Hardal</a> with 
          <a href="https://berkay.fyi" target="_blank">Berkay</a> because marketing analytics 
          had become a mess, and weirdly hard to the marketers 
          who relied on it most. We're fixing that: the best way for accurate data.
        </p>

        <p>
          Outside of building Hardal I'm a curious generalist trying to go deeper. 
          Things I keep coming back to: sailing, surfing, tennis, plants, 
          and the sea in general. Barcelona makes most of these accessible.
        </p>

        <p>
          As mentioned, I don't know a lot of things. This is the website where I share the stuff I'm finding out.
          I'd love to hear from you too.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="contact-line">
        <a href="https://x.com/YOUR_HANDLE" target="_blank">X</a>
        <span class="divider">·</span>
        <a href="https://linkedin.com/in/YOUR_HANDLE" target="_blank">LinkedIn</a>
      </div>
    </main>
    <Footer />
  </body>
</html>

<style>
  .prose {
    max-width: 560px;
  }

  .contact-line {
    margin-top: 3rem;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.75rem;
    font-size: 0.88rem;
  }

  .contact-line a {
    color: var(--text);
    text-decoration: none;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--accent);
    padding-bottom: 1px;
  }

  .contact-line a:hover { color: var(--muted); }

  .divider { color: var(--border); }
</style>
